      <t>This specification adds attributes to EVPN to carry IPv6 address metadata learned from RFC 8505 and RFC 8928 so as to maintain a synchronized copy of the 6LoWPAN ND registrar at each EVPN router and perform locally a unicast IPv6 ND service for address lookup and duplicate address detection.</t>
